{"tid":2358535,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大帽山奇觀「霧淞」動畫解構 明早市區7°C嚴寒 天文台再調低預測","createTime":"2021-01-08T08:03:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-13T05:55:06.000Z","uid":56533,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"00b0bbad5a0d9019fb3989fba8614eca7f6a3599","tid":2358535,"uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T08:03:55.000Z","msg":"寒流再急凍香港，市區氣溫今晨（8日）跌至7.7&deg;C；天文台更調低明早預測至約7&deg;C的嚴寒水平，較之前預測約8&deg;C更低。至於海拔逾950米的大帽山，今晨氣溫跌至-2.5&deg;C，低過除夕強烈寒潮的-1.2&deg;C，創5年新低；草溫亦跌至-1.5&deg;C。《蘋果》記者在大帽山直擊「霧淞」奇觀。2016年1月的強烈寒潮，大帽山氣溫曾跌至-6&deg;C，是1996年有紀錄以來最低；當時都有霧淞。<br />\n<br />\n記者 李鈺廷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QcpoCNF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQcpoCNF.png&h=4a576ceb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MgqrAzF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMgqrAzF.png&h=4f462f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大帽山氣溫和草溫今晨都跌穿冰點一段時間，加上濕度高、風勢清勁，部份植物都凝結上霧淞。《蘋果》記者攝<br />\n<br />\n雖然大帽山草溫在2020年除夕強烈寒潮跌穿冰點，但由於當時太乾燥，加上大風，水汽未能凝結成霜。事隔8日，大帽山草溫和氣溫再次跌穿冰點，雖然同樣風大（昨晚約千米海拔的風勢清勁）而未能廣泛結霜，但因水汽充足（昨晚約千米海拔的相對濕度逾95%），亦能凝結成霧淞或冰。近年形態最美的霧淞，以2010年12月16日最經典，天文台職員當時拍下多幅相片。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bho46GJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBho46GJ.png&h=79320fda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H9Psj1Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH9Psj1Z.png&h=bafd731e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n2010年12月16日，大帽山氣象站附近的鋼纜環，形成羽毛狀霧淞。天文台《氣象冷知識》片段截圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d4bN4t5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd4bN4t5.png&h=3bbf16b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SuuG8VM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSuuG8VM.png&h=5ffc4a93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2010年12月16日，大帽山氣象站附近的水喉開關，形成羽毛狀霧淞。天文台《氣象冷知識》片段截圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/03vK6Jf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F03vK6Jf.jpg&h=421019e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UcePyog.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUcePyog.jpg&h=dec82801&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y4WyfBB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy4WyfBB.jpg&h=5cee3ab7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n料市區一連5日低見7-10&deg;C<br />\n至於今次寒流，天文台仍預測寒冷天氣（市區最低氣溫12&deg;C或以下）會維持7日，預料市區最低氣溫由今日起一連5日都在10&deg;C或以下，明早跌至約7&deg;C，較先前預測約8&deg;C再低一度。天文台電腦預報顯示，新界北部明日普遍會低見約6&deg;C或以下，包括屯門、沙田、大埔和上水，北區打鼓嶺或低至約4&deg;C。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210108/URGATSXR2NEPRJEA5RVHYY3DRQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210108%2FURGATSXR2NEPRJEA5RVHYY3DRQ%2F&d=vGGWHGA7%2F8HunCPhnXLTIeCrFKAYikA6kkEaryQCE%2B8%3D&h=05dc4712\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210108%2FURGATSXR2NEPRJEA5RVHYY3DRQ%2F&h=435a2e73\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210108/URGATSXR2NEPRJEA5RVHYY3DRQ/</a>"},{"pid":"f04f07555d6e2e69b0770485e00671e4f6841104","tid":2358535,"uid":19437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T08:05:47.000Z","msg":"諗起連登涷狗咁既樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"309ded2219f12a7485377e000ecbf71302f9b852","tid":2358535,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T08:09:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_